metadata.name: May The 4th Be With You #1/100
metadata.description:
May the 4th be with you! 

In honor of Star Wars day, I present to you my latest drawing featuring the wise and powerful Master Yoda riding in an AT-AT walker. This iconic scene captures the essence of the Star Wars universe, and I couldn't resist putting my own spin on it. I hope this piece brings a smile to your face and reminds you of the timeless messages of hope, courage, and perseverance that Star Wars has taught us all. May the Force be with you always!

Details:  
Digital: 4961px X 7016px  
Physical: 420mm x 594mm
